</emphasis>
, female. A, habitus, right; B, urosome, ventral; C, left caudal ramus, ventral; D, rostrum; E, antennule; F, antenna; G, labrum; H, mandible; I, paragnath; J, maxillule. Scale bars: A, 0.2 mm; B, D, 0.1 mm; C, E–G, I, J, 0.02 mm; H, 0.05 mm.
</paragraph>
</caption>
<caption id="DF126655EEFF3B9BFF4DF8C3FD5AF88B" ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4591861" ID-Zenodo-Dep="4591861" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4591861/files/figure.png" pageId="430" pageNumber="431" startId="430.[136,245,1805,1831]" targetBox="[199,1404,234,1764]" targetPageId="430">
